saf.core.runtime

Class PluginAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • saf.core.runtime.PluginAttributes

  • public class PluginAttributes
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the attributes and plugin id parsed using the PluginReader. This encapsulates all the attributes contained in a particular plugin file.
    Author:
    Nick Collier
